    <p class="c6"><span class="c1">What is Web Development?</span></p>
    <p class="c6">
        <span class="c2">
            Web development is the process of creating and maintaining websites and web applications. It encompasses several
            aspects, including web design, web content development, client-side/server-side scripting, and network security
            configuration. Web development ranges from creating plain text pages to complex web-based applications, social network
            applications, and electronic business applications.
        </span>
    </p>

